nodes.bodyText:
The uniqueTableName variable name suggests we're making the table name unique, while we're only changing table location.
Let's call the variable tableNameForLocation
Since same naming problem applies to generateUniqueTableName, let's inline that method.
String tableNameForLocation = tableName;
if (useUniqueTableLocation) {
    tableNameForLocation += "-" + randomUUID().toString().replace("-", "")
}

